\[
\Delta H_{\text{sub}}=\Delta_f H^\ominus_{\text{I}_2(g)}-\Delta_f H^\ominus_{\text{I}_2(s)}
\]

The standard enthalpy of formation of solid iodine is zero (element in its standard state), hence  

